ould like you to reflect on the information you just read. Using the space provided below, in your own words, please explain what exactly you learned or what insight this information provided.<br><br>Please try to make your explanation as compelling as possible.<br><\/i>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"n.r","QuestionID":"QID34","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"SL","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"We would like you to reflect on the information you just read. Using the space provided below, in...","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"MinChar","MinChars":"5","TotalChars":"150"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_6EI0MEnaSELekgS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID66","SecondaryAttribute":"We would like you to reflect on the information you just read. Using the space provided below, in...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<i>We would like you to reflect on the information you just read. Using the space provided below, in your own words, please explain what exactly you learned or what insight this information provided.<br><br>Please try to make your explanation as compelling as possible.<br><\/i>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"SL","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"We would like you to reflect on the information you just read. Using the space provided below, in...","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"MinChar","MinChars":"5","TotalChars":"250"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"},"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<i>Please share what you learned from the information provided.<\/i>","DataExportTag":"g.r","QuestionID":"QID66"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_6EI0MEnaSELekgS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1717485716","SecondaryAttribute":"What is your race?","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"What is your race?","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"What is your race?","Choices":{"2":{"Display":"White"},"3":{"Display":"Hispanic, Latino, or Spanish origin"},"4":{"Display":"Black"},"5":{"Display":"Asian"},"6":{"Display":"American Indian or Alaska Native"},"7":{"Display":"Middle Eastern or North African"},"8":{"Display":"Native Hawaiian or Other Pacific Islander"},"9":{"Display":"Some other race, ethnicity, or origin"}},"ChoiceOrder":["2","3","4","5","6","7","8","9"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":10,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"What is your race?","DataExportTag":"Q3","QuestionID":"QID1717485716"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_6EI0MEnaSELekgS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1717485715","SecondaryAttribute":"Which option best aligns with your gender identity?","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Which option best aligns with your gender identity?","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Which option best aligns with your gender identity?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Female"},"2":{"Display":"Male"},"3":{"Display":"Gender Variant\/Non-Conforming"},"4":{"Display":"Not listed"},"5":{"Display":"Prefer not to answer"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2","3","4","5"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":8,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"Which option best aligns with your gender identity?","DataExportTag":"Q2","QuestionID":"QID1717485715"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_6EI0MEnaSELekgS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1717457503","SecondaryAttribute":"You have been invited to participate in a research study conducted by the Cognition & Development...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"You have been invited to participate in a research study conducted by the Cognition &amp; Development Lab at Yale University, about explanations and understanding. The amount of time that we expect this task should take you is indicated in the description of this HIT. There are no known risks to participation in this study, and there are no benefits to participants. You will be compensated for your participation according to the description of this HIT, based on the amount of time this HIT is expected to take. Your participation in this study is voluntary, and you may choose not to participate now or to stop participating at any time. Your responses will be stored securely and only research personnel and those responsible for supervising our research will have access to them. If you have any questions, please feel free to contact the researchers at cognition.development@yale.edu.","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"You have been invited to participate in a research study conducted by the Cognition & Development...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"QuestionText_Unsafe":"You have been invited to participate in a research study conducted by the Cognition &amp; Development Lab at Yale University, about explanations and understanding. The amount of time that we expect this task should take you is indicated in the description of this HIT. There are no known risks to participation in this study, and there are no benefits to participants. You will be compensated for your participation according to the description of this HIT, based on the amount of time this HIT is expected to take. Your participation in this study is voluntary, and you may choose not to participate now or to stop participating at any time. Your responses will be stored securely and only research personnel and those responsible for supervising our research will have access to them. If you have any questions, please feel free to contact the researchers at cognition.development@yale.edu.","DataExportTag":"Q1","QuestionID":"QID1717457503"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_6EI0MEnaSELekgS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID289","SecondaryAttribute":"[insert case]","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<i>[insert case]<\/i>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"[insert case]","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<i>Companies that package their products in ways that superficially resemble those of more fragile products can reduce damages due to shipping.<\/i>","DataExportTag":"case","QuestionID":"QID289"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_6EI0MEnaSELekgS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID332","SecondaryAttribute":"[insert case]","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<i>[insert case]<\/i>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"[insert case]","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<i>[insert case]<\/i>","DataExportTag":"Q332","QuestionID":"QID332"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_6EI0MEnaSELekgS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID214","SecondaryAttribute":"[insert message]","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<i>[insert message]<\/i>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"[insert message]","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<i>Dutch bicycle manufacturer VanMoof found that it had a problem. As it shipped its products to customers, it found that many bicycles were arriving to customers damaged.\n<br><br>The damage reports were a major problem for the company because the company\u2019s bikes are high-end, and some are loaded down with delicate electronics like anti-theft trackers and electric motors. Plus, the company had set a goal to sell 90 percent of its bikes online by the end of the decade.\n<br><br>One of the employees came up with a solution: print a graphic of a flatscreen television on the side of the box. By making shippers think that they were transporting flatscreen televisions, the company found that shipping damage dropped by 70-80 percent. Nobody wants to damage a new television.<\/i>","DataExportTag":"Q214","QuestionID":"QID214"}}]}